node.text: These blog post quotes from Giannis' rookie year really show how far he's come 😢🏆 @giannis_an34

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NBA on ESPN on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

Photo shared by NBA on ESPN on July 22, 2021 tagging @bucks. May be an image of 4 people and text that says '"" When they decided to sign me I was wondering if they would send me to the D-League. And when they decided to keep me I wondered if I would get game time. And when I played, I wanted more. With all that's happened these last months I've come to realize, more and more, that I belong here. GIANNIS ANTETOKOUNMPO in a 2013 blog post (via Sport24)'.

Photo by NBA on ESPN on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 4 people and text that says '"" Did anyone expect I would be here? To be in the starting five of an NBA team? Everyone thought, or almost everyone, that in my first season in the NBA I would be the towel-water-and-ice boy. GIANNIS ANTETOKOUNMPO in a 2013 blog post (via Sport24)'.

Photo by NBA on ESPN on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and text that says '"" LEY-DAVIDSON LAKERS I saw [Kobe] on the bench. He had that killer look, even though he was in his 'civilian' clothes on the bench. I also have that look! Nah, kidding! GIANNIS ANTETOKOUNMPO in a 2013 blog post (via Sport24)'.

Photo by NBA on ESPN on July 22, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people playing sports, ball and text that says '"" AYTON 02 BUCKS 34 BLCKS 34 I try to do all I can on the floor. Play defense for me and my teammates. Close holes and gaps and, at the same time, to get into plays with determination. GIANNIS ANTETOKOUNMPO in a 2013 blog post (via Sport24)'.

Photo shared by NBA on ESPN on July 22, 2021 tagging @easymoneysniper. May be an image of 1 person, playing a sport and text that says '"" QURANT BIGS BINS I have said many times that Durant is my idol. He is the player I watch the most. When I came out on the court for a workout, he was already there, shooting. Working. I stopped and watched him. He was deadly serious... I felt a satisfaction, when I saw my idol, approaching basketball with such determination. GIANNIS ANTETOKOUNMPO in a 2013 blog post (via Sport24)'.

Photo shared by NBA on ESPN on July 22, 2021 tagging @kingjames. May be an image of 7 people, people playing sports and text that says '" wish LAKERS 23 34 In the span of just two days I found myself against two superstars like LeBron and Durant and I got the biggest lessons...LeBron is a two-time champion and four-time MVP. They have both played in SO many AIl Star Games. Even so, work never stops. They do not rest in their glory. They are after perfection. GIANNIS ANTETOKOUNMPO in a 2013 blog post (via Sport24)'.
